    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Species of water plant found in marshy areas from southern and western North America to South America and on Pacific islands. It has tall, thin, dark green stems and woolly brown flowers.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
